ing the mystery behind the angiogenesis pattern. Our results\nmay open up novel bio-sensing and actuating possibilities in medical\ndiagnostics as well as may provide a possible alternative regarding the\ndevelopment of physiologically safe and biocompatible power sources within the\nhuman body.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2019 07:02:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-06"}
