ults\ndemand the inclusion of the kinetics of domain unfolding and refolding in the\nexisting models to account for the relaxation time behaviour.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2019 12:56:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-06"}
